    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including several dents, scratches, and areas of fading paint. Mechanically, the car is currently unreliable and will likely need major repairs to be roadworthy again. The interior also shows heavy signs of use, with stained upholstery and some broken trim pieces. This is a project car for someone looking to invest the time and resources into a full restoration or for parts.",
